In summary, the operando Raman spectroscopy echoes and complements the operando XRD analysis. Both methods demonstrate that the three oxidized Cu precursors (bulk and surface) are fully reduced to metallic Cu when delivering their maximum FEC2+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
